Package: bingAdsR
Type: Package
Title: An interface to Microsoft's Bing API from R 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Deepesh Goel <deepeshgoel.iitk@gmail.com>
Maintainer: The package maintainer <deepeshgoel.iitk@gmail.com>
Description: This package helps user to work on bing ads api in R.
    Currently it supports bing authentication and reporting services only.
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: httr, XML, jsonlite, RCurl
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/deepeshgoeliitk/bingAdsR, https://bingads.microsoft.com, https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/bingads/reporting-service/reporting-service-reference
BugReports: https://github.com/deepeshgoeliitk/bingAdsR/issues
